Agile Model 

Traditional/Waterfall ka problem:  purane tarike mein software ek saath banta tha, months/years lag jaate the, aur end mein user ko product pasand na aaye toh poora paisa aur time barbaad.


Agile kya hai:-

Agile ek iterative approach hai —            bade project ko chote-chote chunks (parts) mein tod dete hain.
1. Har chunk ko ek fixed time period mein deliver karte hain, jise "Sprint" kehte hain (usually 2-4 weeks).
2. Har sprint ke end mein ek working product/feature user ke paas jaata hai.
3. User ka feedback immediately milta hai, aur agle sprint mein improvements daal di jaati hain.


Agile ka fayda:
Fast delivery — har 2 hafte mein kuch na kuch naya user ke haath mein
Requirements badal sakti hain beech mein — flexibility hai
Risk kam hai — kyunki har sprint test hota hai
Customer satisfaction zyada — kyunki woh har step pe involved hai

